  "rationale": "This supervisor prioritizes wall-following on the left, avoids oscillations by consistently preferring right turns for obstacle avoidance, and uses helper commit states to ensure one-shot actions. It is total on uncontrollables, deterministic, and avoids infinite controllable loops. Recovery from obstacles is handled via right turns and full scans if blocked. Forward motion is only allowed when the left wall is present and the path ahead is clear.",
