  "strategy": [
    "Default to moving forward only when the left wall is present and the path ahead is clear.",
    "If an obstacle is detected in front, perform a right turn (rotate_clockwise) to avoid collision.",
    "If the left wall is lost, perform a left turn (rotate_counterclockwise) to re-acquire it.",
    "If blocked after a right turn, perform a full 360-degree scan to find a new path.",
    "Use commit states to ensure one-shot actions and avoid oscillations.",
    "Never enable both rotate directions in the same state.",
    "Transitions on uncontrollable events are total and deterministic.",
    "No infinite controllable loops; all commit actions return to a perception/decision state."
